text:
Feb 5 (Reuters) - Philab Holdings Corp:
* PHILAB HOLDINGS CORP -REFERS TO NEWS ARTICLE “PHILAB TO RAISE UP TO $150 MILLION” PUBLISHED ON FEB 4
* PHILAB HOLDINGS CORP - ALSO REFERS TO NEWS ARTICLE “PHILAB INVESTS IN US-BASED GENOME SEQUENCING COMPANY” PUBLISHED ON FEB 3
* PHILAB HOLDINGS CORP - CO SIGNED DEAL WITH VERITAS GENETICS INTERNATIONAL INVOLVING 3 PHASES; PHASE 1 INVOLVES INVESTMENT BY CO OF $10 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
